Growing up to adolescence, such guys at the first opportunity go to work.
It is difficult if it is bad with knowledge of the language, they admit.
"You feel humiliated and incomplete."
However, in relation to the law on the language, human rights defenders note one important point.
Testing will be carried out only for those migrants who have legal status.
